Join us in a beautiful 10 mile, walk along the Thames Path. You'll explore a
new side of London whilst finding out how to live well.
10 miles, 12 iconic bridges and one great cause.
## **Together, we’re walking for a healthier, happier future**
As well as finding a spring in your step, spending quality time with loved
ones and connecting with nature, we’ll help you find out how to eat, exercise
and live well, with easy to follow wellbeing tips. And, with every step,
you’ll be helping to fund out life-changing research.
By taking part in a Wellness Walk you'll be joining a powerful, positive and
passionate community. You'll be joining others dedicated to supporting people
with diabetes and raising money for a world where diabetes can do no harm.
